headline: Dow's new high ahead of House vote, Trump to host Wall Street execs
summary: Yahoo Finance's John Hyland tracks Wednesday's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including the Dow Jones Industrial Average (^DJI) hitting an intraday record high ahead of the House's vote on a government reopening bill, President Trump reportedly hosting a variety of major Wall Street executives at the White House tonight, Nvidia (NVDA) announcing a $1 billion investment into a Mexico data center, and Bloomberg reporting Disney (DIS) could be exploring an ESPN expansion in Asia. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
